nated the sky since time began, guests will be treated to a celebration of the senses.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr", "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "start", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [], "direction": "ltr", "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "start", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Our highly-experienced culinary team meticulously prepares and serves dishes that are delicately seasoned and deliciously cra\\u001bed, ensuring each bite evokes a taste of history and tradition.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr", "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": "ltr"}}	auto	gold	short	medium	683f1ced65093ff2945f50a6
