8	3	Executive Chef Bin Abbas Said shares insights on the culinary experience at Explorer	34	{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "start", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "We sat down with Executive Chef Bin Abbas Said to discuss how he creates memorable culinary experiences that celebrate his Tanzanian and Zanzibar heritage at the property's multiple dining venues.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr", "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "start", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [], "direction": "ltr", "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "start", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "What types of dishes can guests look forward to at each of the Serengeti Explorer dining venues?", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr", "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 1}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "start", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "We are thrilled to offer a diverse range of dishes that showcase both local flavours and international influences, ensuring a memorable culinary journey for our guests. At Acacia Main Restaurant, we serve specialties like King Fish Steak accompanied by Viazi Vitamu, Mchicha & Tomato Chutney. The traditional Boma offers an authentic African dining experience under the stars, while Kisimani Poolside Bistro & Bar provides refreshing fare, and our intimate Divai chef's table offers a unique dining experience with wine pairings.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr", "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "start", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [], "direction": "ltr", "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "start", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "How do you incorporate local Tanzanian flavours and ingredients into the menus?", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr", "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 1}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "start", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "We take great pride in celebrating the rich culinary heritage of Tanzania, and it's a key focus in our menu development. We source fresh produce from local farmers whenever possible, highlighting seasonal fruits and vegetables such as mchicha, cashew nuts, mangoes, and avocados to create vibrant, flavourful dishes. Our farm-to-table approach ensures freshness while supporting local communities.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr", "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "start", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [], "direction": "ltr", "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "start", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Can you tell us about a signature dish that really represents the Serengeti Explorer experience?", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr", "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 1}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "start", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "The dish that truly embodies the Serengeti Explorer experience is our Grilled Nyama Choma at the Boma Restaurant, served with a side of Kachumbari. This traditional Tanzanian grilled meat dish not only reflects the rich culinary heritage of the region but also embodies the spirit of adventure that the Serengeti represents. Enjoying this authentic dish under the magical African night sky, surrounded by the soft sounds of the Serengeti and the crackle of the Boma fire, creates an unforgettable sensory experience.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr", "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "start", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [], "direction": "ltr", "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "start", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "What's one unexpected or playful twist you've added to the menus that may surprise guests?", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr", "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 1}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "start", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "One element that has garnered quite a bit of excitement is our 'Tanzanian Tasting Journey'—a surprise tasting menu that changes monthly and features playful, modern interpretations of traditional dishes. We've created contemporary presentations of traditional foods that combine Tanzanian flavors with international techniques, offering guests a unique culinary adventure.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr", "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "start", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [], "direction": "ltr", "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "start", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "What makes the sundowner experience and bush breakfasts so special for guests?", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr", "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 1}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "start", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "The sundowner experience offers a unique opportunity for guests to unwind and connect with the breathtaking African landscape at sunset, often accompanied by locally inspired cocktails and snacks. There's something truly magical about sipping a drink while watching the sun set over the Serengeti plains. For our bush breakfasts, we create memorable meals in scenic locations where guests can enjoy fresh food in the heart of the wilderness, creating an immersive experience that connects them with nature.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": "ltr", "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": "ltr", "textFormat": 1}}	\N	\N	\N	2025-06-06 17:12:43.758+03	executive-chef-bin-abbas-said-shares-insights-on-the-culinary-experience-at-explorer	t	2025-06-06 17:12:43.759+03	2025-06-06 17:11:47.424+03	published	2025-06-06 17:12:43.762+03	2025-06-06 17:12:43.765+03	t	f
